    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Large campus provide for good working/ running experience in early morning as it is surrounded by greenary and nature.",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports ground for different sport are available which is very convenient and encourages people to play",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Food provide in canteen is of high quality and we have options to select which ever dish you wish and pay seperately for it , foods that are not popular are also replaced, this is maintained by mess community under DOSA",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Gym and other facilities are also available for public use and is very helpful.",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Multiple groups/ clubs : with multiple groups such as music club , drama club, sports clubs for different games, software (Slashdot) club , hardware club etc so there not a single day wasted.",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good quality education and options are provided for everyone to choose there own path in life ether in extra crecular activities or study related activities. Students are give an opportunity to explore and understand different courses.",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Conditions of hostel is amazing and probably better than any other college",
          "name": "Mohd Sahil Malik",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports facilities are really good with proper maintenance",
          "name": "Mohd Sahil Malik",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty here is really amazing with research background.",
          "name": "Mohd Sahil Malik",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Too much empty space in college, small hostels , snakes, forest.",
          "name": "Soumalya Bera",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "1st year students have to study all 5-6 subjects which I didn't like that much. People who will pursue biology in future have whatsoever no need in maths",
          "name": "Safalya Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our campus could be made more beautiful. Many places are abundant.",
          "name": "Sayan Dasadhikari",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course is good but sometimes tough and except some most of the teachers are good.",
          "name": "Sayan Dasadhikari",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The washing machines are available but are on the payment basis",
          "name": "Ayur raj",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Extreme climate, during winter it can be as cold as 8 degrees celcius and during summer it can go up to 45 degrees Celsius with  a  lot of moisture and humidity causing sweet and can be annoying some times as multiple baths are needed to feel comfort",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some times the rules are followed very strictly and you can be finde 1000 rupees for delay in returning to campus after semester holidays.                                                                                      .",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus too big , although it is a good thing but for daily activities waking to and fro can be a bit too much without bicycle, but it is still manageable                                           .",
          "name": "Md Sohail",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Its is actually very far from the Kolkata city",
          "name": "Mohd Sahil Malik",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
